Importance Points:

1. TestNG is a testing framework developed in the lines of JUnit and NUnit.
2. TestNG is designed to cover all categories of tests: unit, functional, end-to-end, integration, etc.

Prerequisites: 
1. Requires JDK 5 or higher.

